Class Route

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Location>, java.util.Collection<Location>, java.util.List<Location>

    public class Route
extends LocationList
implements java.io.Serializable
    Model class for route Created by Nils on 30.03.2016.

    This class represents a route. Routes are based on LocationList. But have additional attributes like a name, difficulty and routetype.
